page.title: 19MY INTERESTS
page.content: (Alex, age 13): My hobbies include playing my computer, playing cricket, tennis and badminton. The top computer games are now 'Spyhunter', 'Alien 8', 'Ghostbusters' and 'Grand National', a new racing game. Doing well in both the record and computer charts is {BAND AID}the charity to save the starving in Ethiopia. So far over Â£2 million has been raised, and that's without the contributions from other countries like the USA. The best football teams at the moment are Manchester United, Everton, Tottenham Hotspurs and Arsenal, which I support.
